zserio.runtime.array

Interface RawArray

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RawArray.BigIntegerRawArray, RawArray.BitBufferRawArray, RawArray.BooleanRawArray, RawArray.ByteRawArray, RawArray.BytesRawArray, RawArray.DoubleRawArray, RawArray.EnumRawArray, RawArray.FloatRawArray, RawArray.IntRawArray, RawArray.LongRawArray, RawArray.ObjectRawArray, RawArray.ShortRawArray, RawArray.StringRawArray

    public interface RawArray
    Interface for classes which holds raw array. This interface gives the same abstraction for Java native arrays of primitive types like int[] and for Java native arrays of objects. Using the Java native arrays for primitive types is preferred because ArrayList of primitive types wrapper like Integer brings performance penalty during boxing/unboxing.
